<h2 style="font-family:verdana; color:#333">Fact Family Fun</h2>

<div style="line-height:2">
<p style="font-family:verdana; color:#333">A Fact Family can be defined as a group of math facts using the same set of numbers. The fact family shows the relationships between the three numbers involved. These three numbers can be used to form two addition sentences and two subtraction sentences.</p>

<p style="font-family:verdana; color:#333">Select the box then use the number pad on the screen to insert the number. To remove the number in the box, select the box then click the backspace button on the number pad.</p>
</div>